Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.23,0:00:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栗须猛班主任由于生病暂时要休息一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.51,0:00:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是今天开始代课的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽艾老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是丽艾 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽艾酱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位是联谊时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:24.61,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽艾酱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.56,0:02:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量再生 经历了作为僵尸的人生后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 即使世界再残酷 人们也绝不孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大师艾丽艾尔给予了他更为残酷的试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 相川步的战斗远没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:13.85,OT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(260,0)}「但是 那样就好」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在打什么主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川步同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉丝太过危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你很容易被她整的焦头烂额的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 春奈的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉丝是我的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经做好了挑战她的觉悟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 相川同学就必须成为强大的魔装少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,测验？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是不合格的话就要被消除记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪边开始的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:55.15,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我也？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌讨厌 哥哥 要忘了优了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:59.78,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是内心脆弱的主角相川步的脑补声音 CV：佐久间玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.81,0:03:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要抹杀掉你的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会被强制送还的吧 绝对要合格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不知道该干什么怎么干才好 别强人所难了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是今天开始担任你们老师的春奈 关照关照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来做老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春奈酱是老师来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常有教我做煎蛋 原来是老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害 以我为中心开始逐渐完成的后宫建造
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.31,0:03:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 今天来学习针对煎蛋的科学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 在教科书的第几页
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春奈的课是活的 不需要教科书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太明白天才说的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子到了这边之后变得相当开朗了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是受到了步的影响吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在烧杯里放进鸡蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下就能知道春奈老师的煎蛋做法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停的搅拌至黏稠后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放入类似于贤者之石一样的玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的话作为代替品放入粘土橡皮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用这个代替啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用马赫速度 搅拌大约30分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春奈老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 煎蛋跟史莱姆的生成方法很像 仅差分毫而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事第一次听说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然成功炼成这么大只的史莱姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春奈真是优秀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 送福利的史莱姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的 只会融化掉衣服而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是专业送福利的史莱姆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看啦 变态 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说这种事的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春奈老师 黏黏的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 学生们…怎怎怎怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下了袜子跟内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是位绅士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立马就遇到危机了呢 怎么办 步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我见识一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是僵尸 人类的极限什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太绅士了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:05:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妙子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妙子 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三原 手伸过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来 真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:14.10,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说这种话的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织户
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僵尸步 我明明是想帮助你才做老师的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 待着别动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 赤身裸体的你乱摸什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 别闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太绅士了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛 眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大师 万分感激
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明到中途为止表现还挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么像你们这样奇怪的人会在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:26.72,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丧失记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僵尸步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我叫相川步的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僵尸步就叫僵尸步嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是变成这样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯独这件事是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说继续让相川同学遭遇危险反而不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僵尸步遇到危险才是正道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话说的… 不过也没错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不走也没关系啊 总有这么一种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僵尸步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难办了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想把在这度过的时间当做是白白浪费的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:26.03,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家跟步一起度过的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大师 求求你 别让僵尸步忘了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶还没喝完
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁这段时间 来场补考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追加考试
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要大家直接接触步本人并想方设法直做点什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:09:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步的记忆应该就可以恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.22,0:09:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是不负责任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得正是因为她身上所背负的责任过于重大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会这么冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和路塞伊斯大人 你能说话了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 我们是脱离了躯体枷锁的精神体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以心意相通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法 真是奇妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僵尸步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是十分抱歉 好像我的本体给各位添了很多麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是勉强保留下来的 过去的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 优库里伍德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让你成为独当一面的魔装少女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的小事不轻松地做到可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真是和你本人一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个什么样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是只蛆虫喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个蛋疼的舞台是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最终boss的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:47.17,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JRPG=Japanese RPG
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我的中二病不轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能到达这里啊 愚蠢的鼠辈们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大人的名字是阿斯莫德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:03.06,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是相川步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.42,0:11:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Asmodeus是掌管淫欲的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是优库里伍德 甚是博学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是淫欲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:22.45,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是相川步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是别西卜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾名为贝黑摩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中二病
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我的头又痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路西法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:30.21,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是相川步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利未安森
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再自曝下去了 实在太惨不忍睹了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 简直是恶魔级的令人作呕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒旦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 确实很符合步的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 我是这种人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痒 背上鸡皮疙瘩起个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着自己的分身终于知道自己有多恶心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些人怎么样都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:12:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来取回步的记忆的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是位勇敢的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等是身负大罪的相川步之化身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为能打得倒我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让我稍微享受一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下 别再说下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能让他们老实下来 就可以接触到步的心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我上了 你们这些混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是精神体的话 应该可以变身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「虽然我可爱又迷人 但我会招来死亡」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好弱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是步的精神嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:12:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 确实这样才像他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为这样就赢了 我等即为开始 亦是结束…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}停下 别再说下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始觉得有点烦躁了 赶紧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僵尸步 你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是僵尸步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 回去咯 记得要感谢我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 赶紧回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫贝尔菲戈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淫欲 贪婪什么的不过是喽啰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:14:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川步真正的本体正是我 贝尔菲戈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Belphegor 掌管着懒惰的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:05.53,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懒惰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说失去了干劲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 越来越觉得这货就是步了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本就只想平静度日而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果呢 和你们相识之后终日鸡犬不宁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的步并没有那么想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是多么优秀的魔法师都无法探究出人的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到今天为止我究竟为你们费了多少心 你明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你顾虑我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川步他啊 是个纯朴的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是说一句「好吧」就可以放下别人不管的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那也只是到今天为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起 我就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川步了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步 记忆恢复了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾名贝尔菲戈尔 另一个我（another）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个…步？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以说是另一个可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生的我（alternative）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好绕口 就叫你黑化步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你至今把我耍的团团转的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然从内衣可以看出一个人的本性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 色欲的性格暴露太多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情感这种东西看来是无法完全抑制住的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来春奈她们是失败了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始我要自由地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我要去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 刚才看了小裤裤 等会宰了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僵尸步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚出门了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那令人蛋疼的性格就留在身体里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:26.92,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在价值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊 那令人蛋疼的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…相川吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 做什么都好烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连活着也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天比以往更严重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 又有什么新想法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 世界上不能被知道的秘密在增加着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们什么都不知道真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去医务室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的相川同学状况好像不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.14,0:17:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家最好不要太刺激他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川同学 等一下请到办公室来一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我是坏人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春奈同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费人家的一片好心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去魔力的你能做得了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:41.50,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来做对手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优做对手？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧 我可是喜欢你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是喜欢 究竟是like还是love先卖个关子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.75,0:17:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋疼蛋疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住口 相川
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再用那种语气说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话 给我到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要在这里战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细想想 看来我跟操场真有缘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为发生了什么 狗屎达令有点奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的相川 我不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:29.92,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可悲 为什么要争斗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是命运吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 那是什么台词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我倒觉得挺有他的风格的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:43.69,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我可爱又迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:47.57,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我会招来死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.08,0:19:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 死灵师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那奇怪的僵尸步打的四脚朝天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷　300%
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可爱啊 优
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我喜欢的步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 不写出来我不懂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和我一起来也可以哦 优
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:53.13,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆鳞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆鳞？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会有问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是拜你所赐成为僵尸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:21.78,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:22.91,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有肉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的便条
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:27.67,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:29.17,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要再做了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:30.79,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 我是 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭 死灵师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要唤回原来的步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僵尸步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我僵尸步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是another　或者叫我alternative
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦人 你就是个僵尸步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:13.09,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来吧 步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛…住手 春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.97,0:21:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回来 步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.01,0:21:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僵尸步 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有话要说啊 蛆虫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.05,0:22:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 能帮我把下半身捡过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下半身 你是变态啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.86,0:22:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是让人恶心的无话可说的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.23,0:22:15.23,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都是个奇怪的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.37,0:22:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补考就算勉强合格了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.49,0:22:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然大部分人会毫无察觉地度过一生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.01,0:22:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是世界上存在着许多绝对不能被知道的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.57,0:22:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川步 明明是人类 却好像好有趣的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉吵到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了那些之后 就再也没办法回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是宁宁 就连艾丽艾尔也照顾着相川啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.44,0:22:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被选中的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.55,0:23:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 克莉丝我会带走他的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.90,0:23:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 助手减少了 会头疼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.24,0:23:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有这么多有趣的人们 我又怎么可能把自己置身事外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.97,0:23:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的记忆也回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.48,0:23:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春奈也可以留在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.01,0:23:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步 你这个呆瓜脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.92,0:23:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说的好像是我想跟你住在一起似的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.76,0:23:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是个令人作呕的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果不是这样的话 就不是相川步了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变回往常的样子虽然好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.53,0:23:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但麻烦的事就是麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.33,0:23:54.83,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.80,0:23:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.44,0:24:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终话了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.27,0:24:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要结束啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.84,0:24:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周也放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.97,0:24:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束是新的开始 不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.58,0:24:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,净说些漂亮话来掩盖现实
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.35,0:24:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家 不要忘记我们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.88,0:24:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一直为我们加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.26,0:24:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你还记得我们 就不算是完结
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.36,0:24:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又说着更漂亮的话想蒙混过去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.04,0:24:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.41,0:24:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
